After hes killed by the righteous leader of his own guild, Woojin gets a chance to start over. This time hes not interested in saving the world from monstershes got his sights set on revenge! His high-level kills quickly garner him notoriety among the game plebs, while boosting his stats as he masterminds his way closer to the top. But there's something no one can figure out: whose side hes playing for. Now that he knows how to play to win, Woojin will stop at nothing to destroy the hero!
(Source: Tapas)

Lee Hojae had given up his life as a pro gamer, until one day he received a mysterious message: Congratulations! Youve been invited to the Tutorial World. Intrigued, he enters the game and confidently chooses hell difficulty, but soon learns that he is trapped there. With a mere 0.01% survival rate, Hojae must somehow overcome the games agonizing challenges to figure out the real reason he was invited. This tutorial may be tough, but its secrets are whats truly hellacious. (Source: Tapas)
